<HEAD>Jury Rules For Valerie Harper In Dispute Over `Valerie' Series</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: SUBS grafs 6-7, `Miss Harper ..., with 7 grafs to UPDATE with
comment from jury foreman, Lorimar spokeswoman, new quotes from
